2 CONC &gt;1854-55 THE TEXAS SCHOLASTICS: J. Thomas paid school tax in District 14 of Grimes County for 2 males and 1 female (John, Samuel, Phoebe) Nelson B. Thomas paid a school tax in District 4 of Montgomery County for 6 children. In 1855, Mary Thoma
